There are very simple ways by which you have
to correct your left or right side and to

00:41:05.312 --> 00:41:07.901
be in the center.

00:41:07.901 --> 00:41:10.732
And then when you are in the center the growth
take place.

00:41:10.732 --> 00:41:17.062
Is very simple and luckily we are going to
