This is at a humane awareness.

00:43:39.122 --> 00:43:43.151
But at the spiritual awareness you become
beyond sufferings.

00:43:43.151 --> 00:43:49.252
And Christ is to be awakened within you, that’s
the points is.

00:43:49.252 --> 00:43:50.732
Because Christ is not awakened within you.

00:43:50.732 --> 00:43:59.882
When the Christ, you know, in this chakra
– this center is Agya chakra, here – is

00:43:59.882 --> 00:44:02.662
bestowed the Deity of Christ.

00:44:02.662 --> 00:44:08.222
Now here if you can see in the map there is
they have shown on one side the ego, another

00:44:08.222 --> 00:44:11.612
side – the superego, means the conditioning.

00:44:11.612 --> 00:44:19.552
Now when this chakra is awakened meaning the
Christ within us is awakened, then He sucks

00:44:19.552 --> 00:44:20.812
in our karmas.

00:44:20.812 --> 00:44:25.402
That’s why they say that He died for our
sins.

00:44:25.402 --> 00:44:31.392
Then He also sucks in our conditioning, both
the things.

00:44:31.392 --> 00:44:42.282
He is placed in the middle of the brain you
can say where is the optic chaisma crossing

00:44:42.282 --> 00:44:48.072
and He looks after the pituitary and the pineal
body.

00:44:48.072 --> 00:44:53.752
That’s how He controls both the things within
us and He sucks in.

00:44:53.752 --> 00:44:57.072
And when He sucks in there’s an opening
that takes place on our fontanel bone area

00:44:57.072 --> 00:44:58.282
and through that then the Kundalini pierces
through.

00:44:58.282 --> 00:44:59.312
Q. [NOT AUDIBLE]

00:44:59.312 --> 00:45:10.342
The Sahaja Yogi: How can you keep your Self-Realization
if you are not in touch with the collective?

00:45:10.342 --> 00:45:26.164
Shri Mataji: You can not.

00:45:26.164 --> 00:45:28.332
You have to keep some connection with the
collective.

00:45:28.332 --> 00:45:31.082
It’s like say nowadays it’s autumn you
have seen.

00:45:31.082 --> 00:45:32.891
In autumn what happens?

00:45:32.891 --> 00:45:40.392
A bark like a cork develops between the leaves
and the tree.

00:45:40.392 --> 00:45:43.462
And such a leaf falls off and dies.

00:45:43.462 --> 00:45:48.302
You have to be in the collective, you can
not keep your Self-Realization without collectivity.

00:45:48.302 --> 00:45:51.432
Is very important to be with the collective.

00:45:51.432 --> 00:45:57.012
This is one point people fail, because they
think they’ll lose their individuality.

00:45:57.012 --> 00:45:58.682
Is a wrong idea.

00:45:58.682 --> 00:46:01.782
Actually when the leaf dies it has no individuality.

00:46:01.782 --> 00:46:07.651
On the contrary, when it is on the tree you’ll
be surprised, that one leaf can not tally

00:46:07.651 --> 00:46:10.392
with another leaf in the whole world.

00:46:10.392 --> 00:46:15.132
Such an individual thing it is.

00:46:15.132 --> 00:46:21.442
It is I would say unity in diversity, complete
unity in diversity.

00:46:21.442 --> 00:46:25.712
Because that is the variety is the one that
gives beauty to this world.

00:46:25.712 --> 00:46:30.612
Otherwise if we are all sort of dressed of
the same way, walking the same way, it will

00:46:30.612 --> 00:46:32.582
be such a boring company.

00:46:47.938 --> 00:46:50.338
Is there any question?

00:46:50.363 --> 00:46:52.490
Such a rapport.

00:46:52.515 --> 00:46:53.982
It’s beautiful people today.

00:46:54.095 --> 00:46:54.838
All right.

00:46:54.855 --> 00:46:59.275
So now, as I’ve requested you, those who
would like to go, should go.

00:46:59.377 --> 00:47:05.507
Because when we do this we all have to close
the eyes and people are not even willing to

00:47:05.507 --> 00:47:06.507
do that.

00:47:06.507 --> 00:47:11.307
So the thing is that the Divine is not going
to fall at out feet, isn’t it?

00:47:11.307 --> 00:47:12.927
We have to be little humble about it.

00:47:12.927 --> 00:47:19.627
If we don’t have that humility is better
we should try other methods and then come

00:47:19.627 --> 00:47:20.967
to Sahaja Yoga.

00:47:20.967 --> 00:47:28.787
Because Sahaja Yoga is not meant for arrogant
people, for people who think knowing of themselves.

00:47:28.787 --> 00:47:41.297
Is meant for people who want to get their
Self-Realization.

00:47:41.297 --> 00:47:49.167
Now a simple thing we have to do, all of us,
which is also sometimes not liked by people

00:47:49.167 --> 00:47:52.977
when I tell them – we have to take out our
shoes.

00:47:52.977 --> 00:47:56.427
Because this Mother Earth is going to help
us a lot.

00:47:56.427 --> 00:47:58.907
She’s the one who is giver of everything.

00:47:58.907 --> 00:48:02.576
So we have to take out our shoes and touch
the Mother Earth.

00:48:02.576 --> 00:48:16.847
You can keep your socks on with your both
the feet.

00:48:27.285 --> 00:48:34.599
Put both the feet separately because there
are two powers separately on the Mother Earth.

00:48:51.192 --> 00:48:56.527
Those who are sitting on the ground are all
right as they are, they need not put their

00:48:56.527 --> 00:49:06.437
feet like this, they can sit in a Sahaja asana,
means in a way that is relaxed, not to put

00:49:06.437 --> 00:49:08.897
legs on top of another row or anything.

00:49:08.897 --> 00:49:11.607
Any stress on your body is not needed.

00:49:11.607 --> 00:49:17.576
You have to be comfortable to be straight,
sitting straight, not putting your neck back

00:49:17.576 --> 00:49:27.296
or forward, just sitting straight, that’s
all.

00:49:27.296 --> 00:49:34.777
One promise has to be there in your heart,
that you will after Realization respect your

00:49:34.777 --> 00:49:43.487
Realization and grow like a tree and should
not be the like the parable of the seeds that

00:49:43.487 --> 00:49:50.027
some seeds fell on a rock and some who sprouted
also got lost.

00:49:50.027 --> 00:49:57.887
I would request you very-very earnestly and
with a great concern that you have to look

00:49:57.887 --> 00:50:01.517
after your Self-Realization and your growth.

00:50:01.517 --> 00:50:10.377
As we do not take any money from anyone, we
don’t have very elaborate places or elaborate

00:50:10.377 --> 00:50:15.277
centers, so whatever is available is there
for you.

00:50:15.277 --> 00:50:22.277
But that is God’s place and you have to
come there to get all the information, the

00:50:22.277 --> 00:50:26.857
knowledge about the Self.

00:50:26.857 --> 00:50:39.707
I hope you will not treat it with just a side
issue, but the main object of your human

00:50:39.707 --> 00:50:41.469
ascent.

00:50:42.668 --> 00:50:47.907
You don’t have to pay for it; you don’t
have to do anything else.

00:50:47.907 --> 00:50:58.027
Moreover, we are all the time trying to save
time and that is why the time has to be spent

00:50:58.027 --> 00:51:03.297
is been collective and enjoying the joy.

00:51:03.297 --> 00:51:08.647
May God bless you all.

00:51:09.519 --> 00:51:12.949
So both hands have to be like this, to begin
with.

00:51:14.117 --> 00:51:21.843
This is because as I told you these are all
sympathetic centers which are to be enlightened

00:51:21.843 --> 00:51:25.934
first of all, so the information goes to the
Kundalini that the Kundalini is to be awakened.

00:51:25.950 --> 00:51:28.251
This is first thing we have to do.

00:51:28.276 --> 00:51:37.370
Now, secondly, we have to facilitate the movement
of the Kundalini even if she’s awakened.

00:51:37.370 --> 00:51:45.830
And for that I will tell you how to put your
hand into various centers to the various centers

00:51:45.830 --> 00:51:49.352
so that you can yourself facilitate.

00:51:49.377 --> 00:51:53.620
I would like one of you to get up and show
this better.

00:51:53.620 --> 00:51:55.320
Yeah.

00:51:55.320 --> 00:52:02.340
Now Dr. Spiro will show you also and I will
also that first you have to put your hand

00:52:02.340 --> 00:52:04.100
to your heart where resides.

00:52:04.100 --> 00:52:08.430
Now left hand towards Me and right hand on
the heart.

00:52:08.430 --> 00:52:11.540
Left hand towards Me.

00:52:11.540 --> 00:52:16.910
Now to your heart and here resides the Spirit.

00:52:16.910 --> 00:52:23.380
We work only on the left hand side, because
that is the side of our desire and put the

00:52:23.380 --> 00:52:30.880
left hand like this symbolically meaning that
this is the power of desire and we want to

00:52:30.880 --> 00:52:34.970
have our Self-Realization, expression of that.

00:52:34.970 --> 00:52:44.600
Now the second chakra is on the upper part
of your abdomen on the left hand side.

00:52:44.600 --> 00:52:56.570
This is the center of your mastery by which
the mastery over this power of love or Divine

00:52:56.570 --> 00:53:00.650
vibrations you achieve and manifest through
your being.

00:53:00.650 --> 00:53:04.840
Is just starts working like through our eyes
we can see the light.

00:53:04.840 --> 00:53:13.340
In the same way, once you become the master,
you can feel, you can know everything about

00:53:13.340 --> 00:53:16.570
yourself and about others.

00:53:16.570 --> 00:53:26.640
Then you have to take down your right hand
to the lower part of your abdomen.

00:53:26.640 --> 00:53:36.790
This is the one, which is working out our
pure knowledge, knowledge, which is absolute

00:53:36.790 --> 00:53:38.060
and pure.

00:53:38.060 --> 00:53:44.810
This center is very important and by some
unauthorized people if some people have tamper

00:53:44.810 --> 00:53:51.130
it we have to nourish it by putting our right
hand towards it.

00:53:51.130 --> 00:53:58.860
Then again we go back into the upper part
of the abdomen.

00:53:58.860 --> 00:54:01.380
Then we go back to our heart.

00:54:01.380 --> 00:54:12.130
Now here we go back to the left hand side
of our neck, here, like this from front.

00:54:12.130 --> 00:54:14.570
Many people tried this side (Shri Mataji pointed
to the back side of Her neck).

00:54:14.570 --> 00:54:15.570
No.

00:54:15.570 --> 00:54:21.040
You have to try from front and then turn your
head to your right, like this.

00:54:21.040 --> 00:54:30.489
Now this center catches when we feel guilty
and now I find quite a lot catching in this

00:54:30.489 --> 00:54:31.489
audience.

00:54:31.489 --> 00:54:39.210
So please for the sake of your Self-Realization
forgive yourself, forgive yourself, forgive

00:54:39.210 --> 00:54:40.210
yourself.

00:54:40.210 --> 00:54:48.310
Now, please now stretch your hand like this
and put it on top of your forehead.

00:54:48.310 --> 00:54:53.140
This is the center of forgiveness, – here.

00:54:53.140 --> 00:54:55.700
And press it on both the sides, like this.

00:54:55.700 --> 00:55:04.322
Now you have to take this hand on the back,
rest your head on that, put the head up.

00:55:04.322 --> 00:55:16.030
And then you have to take out your hand again
and stretch it like this.

00:55:16.030 --> 00:55:17.080
Fully stretched.

00:55:17.080 --> 00:55:22.790
The center of your palm is to be placed on
top of the fontanel bone area.

00:55:22.790 --> 00:55:25.240
You might bend your head a little, would be
better.

00:55:25.240 --> 00:55:34.560
Just there, which was a soft bone in your
childhood, and you have to press your scalp

00:55:34.560 --> 00:55:41.340
and move it about seven times slowly in a
clockwise manner.

00:55:41.340 --> 00:55:52.940
That’s all we have to do.

00:55:52.940 --> 00:55:58.530
But we must press it hard and the fingers
must be pushed back nicely so that we can

00:55:58.530 --> 00:56:01.020
press our palm nicely.

00:56:01.020 --> 00:56:02.270
All right.

00:56:02.270 --> 00:56:06.530
That’s all is to be done.

00:56:06.530 --> 00:56:10.090
[INAUDIBLE WORD – Principally ?]

00:56:10.090 --> 00:56:12.239
Now we have to close our eyes.

00:56:12.239 --> 00:56:15.870
Please don’t open your eyes till I’ll
tell you.

00:56:15.870 --> 00:56:24.200
Because the attention will be attracted inside
and please you can take out your glasses.

00:56:24.200 --> 00:56:28.790
The other day one lady who was quite blind
I think and she started seeing this, I mean,

00:56:28.790 --> 00:56:33.239
you know, things happen like that.

00:56:33.239 --> 00:56:35.960
I would request you to take out your glasses.

00:56:35.960 --> 00:56:36.980
It helps you.

00:56:36.980 --> 00:56:42.780
And you keep your eyes shut till I’ll tell
you, please don’t open your eyes.

00:56:42.780 --> 00:56:51.510
It is how you are going to help yourself and
also you will know how to all the time raise

00:56:51.510 --> 00:56:53.320
your Kundalini.

00:56:53.320 --> 00:57:00.560
It’s very simple method, which I’m telling
you.

00:57:00.560 --> 00:57:07.430
Now, please put your left hand towards Me
like this and right hand on your heart.

00:57:07.430 --> 00:57:13.979
Left hand towards Me and right hand on your
heart.

00:57:13.979 --> 00:57:17.260
Here, now close your eyes.

00:57:17.260 --> 00:57:20.070
In the heart resides the Spirit.

00:57:20.070 --> 00:57:25.530
So please ask Me question within yourself,
a very fundamental question, you can call

00:57:25.530 --> 00:57:32.640
Me Shri Mataji or Mother, whatever you like,
“Mother, am I the Spirit?”

00:57:32.640 --> 00:57:37.469
Ask this question, “Mother, am I the Spirit?”

00:57:37.469 --> 00:57:44.715
Is a very fundamental question here to ask.

00:57:44.779 --> 00:57:50.249
Ask this question three times.

00:57:50.249 --> 00:57:58.229
Now, if you are the Spirit, you are also your
guide and master.

00:57:58.229 --> 00:58:04.890
Please put your right hand in the upper part
of your abdomen on the left hand side, on

00:58:04.890 --> 00:58:15.650
your stomach on the left hand side and press
it hard and ask a question here three times

00:58:15.650 --> 00:58:20.020
again, “Mother, am I my own master?

00:58:20.020 --> 00:58:23.700
Mother, am I my own master?

00:58:23.700 --> 00:58:27.630
Mother, am I my own master?”

00:58:27.630 --> 00:58:33.960
Ask this question in your heart.

00:58:33.960 --> 00:58:50.270
Now, we move our right hand, move it down
into the lower part of your abdomen on the

00:58:50.270 --> 00:58:51.450
left hand side.

00:58:51.450 --> 00:58:58.860
Now here, please keep your eyes shut, please
keep your eyes shut and don’t move too much.

00:58:58.860 --> 00:59:10.360
Here you have to know that I respect your
freedom and I can not force you to have the

00:59:10.360 --> 00:59:11.450
pure knowledge.

00:59:11.450 --> 00:59:15.270
You have to say that you want it.

00:59:15.270 --> 00:59:26.636
So here you please say, “Mother, please
give me pure knowledge” six times, because

00:59:26.661 --> 00:59:29.336
this center has got six petals.

00:59:29.361 --> 00:59:39.261
So please say six times, “Mother, please
give me pure knowledge”.

00:59:44.530 --> 00:59:53.856
With this asking the Kundalini starts rising,
because she knows you want it.

00:59:54.142 --> 01:00:03.860
Now to facilitate her movement we go back
to the higher chakra and take our hand to

01:00:03.860 --> 01:00:09.633
the upper part of the abdomen on the left
hand side and press it hard.

01:00:09.658 --> 01:00:21.001
Now, with full confidence we have to say ten
times, “Mother, I am my own master”.

01:00:21.026 --> 01:00:28.197
Say it with full confidence so the Kundalini
will rise, “Mother, I am my own master”.

01:00:28.284 --> 01:00:32.580
Please say it ten times.

01:00:32.580 --> 01:00:45.407
This will correct your spiritual domination
if somebody has dominated you spiritually

01:00:45.432 --> 01:00:50.312
in the sense that they have misguided you
spiritually.

01:00:50.312 --> 01:00:55.142
“I am my own master”.

01:00:55.142 --> 01:01:11.582
Now, raise your right hand to the heart.

01:01:11.607 --> 01:01:15.887
Here resides the Spirit.

01:01:18.412 --> 01:01:34.002
So with full confidence say twelve times,
“Mother, I am the Spirit”.

01:01:34.002 --> 01:01:35.538
Have confidence in yourself.

01:01:35.563 --> 01:01:44.460
We have to know, that the Divine is the ocean
of love and compassion.

01:01:44.485 --> 01:01:54.032
But above all it is the ocean of forgiveness
and we can not commit any mistakes, which

01:01:54.032 --> 01:01:59.082
the Divine can not forgive.

01:01:59.082 --> 01:02:10.917
So please forgive yourself, forgive yourself
fully, and raise your right hand in the corner

01:02:10.942 --> 01:02:17.211
of your neck and your shoulder, and turn your
head to the right.

01:02:17.236 --> 01:02:29.222
And here with full confidence you say sixteen
times, “Mother, I am not guilty at all”.

01:02:29.222 --> 01:02:35.182
Please say it, very important and as I said,
if you still feel guilty, you can punish yourself

01:02:35.182 --> 01:02:38.322
by saying it hundred and eight times.

01:02:38.347 --> 01:02:45.028
You have to be pleasantly placed towards yourself
because you are going to enter into the Kingdom

01:02:45.053 --> 01:02:47.290
of God.

01:02:50.678 --> 01:02:55.953
You have to love yourself and respect yourself.

01:02:56.247 --> 01:03:17.877
Sixteen times please say it.

01:03:22.751 --> 01:03:31.461
Now raise your hand and put it on your forehead
across.

01:03:31.461 --> 01:03:36.461
Put it on your forehead across.

01:03:36.461 --> 01:03:40.661
This is the center of forgiveness.

01:03:40.661 --> 01:03:52.345
So please here
you have to say, “Mother, I forgive everyone”,

01:03:52.370 --> 01:03:54.140
from your heart.

01:03:55.411 --> 01:03:59.791
You might say it is difficult, but it is a
myth.

01:03:59.791 --> 01:04:04.280
Whether you forgive or you do not forgive
you do not do anything.

01:04:04.280 --> 01:04:08.010
But if you do not forgive then you play into
wrong hands.

01:04:08.010 --> 01:04:15.250
So to get over all the loads you just say
from your heart, “Mother, I forgive everyone”.

01:04:15.250 --> 01:04:20.280
It’s not important how many times.

01:04:20.280 --> 01:04:25.851
Press it on both the sides please.

01:04:25.851 --> 01:04:43.116
Now take back your hand, and put your hand
on the back of your head, and raise your head

01:04:43.155 --> 01:04:44.187
on that.

01:04:44.417 --> 01:04:47.111
Move your head upward.

01:04:47.111 --> 01:04:56.051
Now here for your own satisfaction only, without
counting any mistakes or guilt you can say,

01:04:56.051 --> 01:05:03.681
“Oh, Divine, if I have made any mistakes,
please forgive me”.

01:05:03.681 --> 01:05:08.050
For your own satisfaction, don’t feel guilty
about it.

01:05:08.075 --> 01:05:11.764
In a very pleasant manner.

01:05:17.571 --> 01:05:32.530
Now stretch your hand fully, push back your
fingers, and put the center of your palm on

01:05:32.530 --> 01:05:42.851
top of the fontanel bone area, and now start
moving it very slowly, very slowly clockwise

01:05:42.851 --> 01:05:43.931
the scalp.

01:05:43.931 --> 01:05:46.541
Press it hard, push back your fingers.

01:05:46.541 --> 01:05:47.541
Seven times.

01:05:47.541 --> 01:05:54.581
At this point I must say that I can not force
again the Self-Realization upon you.

01:05:54.581 --> 01:05:56.861
I respect your freedom.

01:05:56.861 --> 01:05:58.551
You have to ask for it.

01:05:58.551 --> 01:06:08.190
So please say seven times, “Mother, please
give me my Realization, give me my Self-Realization”.

01:06:08.215 --> 01:06:11.339
Or, “May I have my Self-Realization”.

01:06:12.712 --> 01:07:14.291
(Shri Mataji is blowing in the microphone
7 times.)

01:07:14.291 --> 01:07:20.780
Now please take down your hands.

01:07:20.780 --> 01:07:28.270
Please open your eyes very slowly.

01:07:28.270 --> 01:07:30.701
Now watch Me without thinking.

01:07:30.701 --> 01:07:33.181
Let’s see if you can do it.

01:07:33.181 --> 01:07:34.471
Without thinking.

01:07:34.471 --> 01:07:39.750
Just watch Me without thinking.

01:07:39.750 --> 01:07:47.061
Please put your right hand towards Me, right
hand towards Me like this.

01:07:47.061 --> 01:07:55.321
And the left hand above your head and bend
your head and try to see if you are feeling

01:07:55.321 --> 01:07:57.341
any cool breeze from here.

01:07:57.341 --> 01:07:59.871
Bend your head, bend, bend it.

01:08:12.065 --> 01:08:13.169
Little higher.

01:08:13.201 --> 01:08:15.944
Some people get it very high, very high they
get it, some of them.

01:08:15.969 --> 01:08:18.079
Move it.

01:08:19.326 --> 01:08:25.926
And now put the left hand towards Me like
this, again bend your head and see if you

01:08:25.926 --> 01:08:39.285
are getting a cool breeze in your head.

01:08:39.285 --> 01:08:46.108
Now put your right hand towards Me again,
bend your head and see for yourself again

01:08:46.133 --> 01:08:50.403
if there’s a cool breeze.

01:08:59.954 --> 01:09:10.656
Now raise both your hands towards the sky
and push back your head and ask a question

01:09:10.656 --> 01:09:16.546
three times, “Mother, is this the cool breeze
of the Holy Ghost?

01:09:16.546 --> 01:09:18.666
Mother, is this the Brahma Shakti?

01:09:18.666 --> 01:09:22.504
Mother, is this the All Pervading Power of
God’s Love?”

01:09:22.529 --> 01:09:27.004
Just ask the question.

01:09:30.626 --> 01:09:33.348
Now put down your hands.

01:09:33.373 --> 01:09:36.023
Now please put your hands like this.

01:09:43.356 --> 01:09:48.916
You’ll feel very relaxed and peaceful.

01:09:48.916 --> 01:09:52.876
In the hands also you’ll feel little cool
breeze coming.

01:09:52.876 --> 01:09:58.775
Some people might feel in one hand, might
feel in another hand.

01:09:58.775 --> 01:10:02.805
Some of them do feel that way.

01:10:02.805 --> 01:10:19.865
All those who are feeling the cool breeze
on top of their heads or on their fingertips,

01:10:19.865 --> 01:10:23.813
please raise both your hands.

01:10:24.043 --> 01:10:32.285
Both hands to be raised those who are feeling
it.

01:10:32.285 --> 01:10:37.745
Just imagine!

01:10:37.745 --> 01:10:40.826
Most of them have felt it.

01:10:40.826 --> 01:10:42.045
Imagine.

01:10:42.045 --> 01:10:44.496
Hardly very few haven’t felt.

01:10:44.496 --> 01:10:53.015
It’s very easy for them also to feel it
and if they want they can come up to the stage

01:10:53.015 --> 01:10:54.955
and people can look after them.

01:10:54.955 --> 01:11:02.095
They can feel it today, they should and they
will work out their Kundalini.

01:11:02.095 --> 01:11:10.342
Maybe little help is needed and it’s very
kind of you, all of you to have received your

01:11:10.367 --> 01:11:11.842
Realization.

01:11:11.867 --> 01:11:14.382
I bow to all of you.

01:11:14.572 --> 01:11:21.665
I bow to all of you and I beg of you as a
Mother that please look after your Self-Realization,

01:11:21.665 --> 01:11:24.115
do not waste it.

01:11:24.115 --> 01:11:30.375
Those who haven’t got it should not feel
in any way disturbed or upset, it’s very

01:11:30.375 --> 01:11:31.526
simple.

01:11:31.526 --> 01:11:37.026
Maybe the little time was needed more or whatever
it is.

01:11:37.026 --> 01:11:41.615
I would request them to come on the stage
for five minutes or ten minutes and they might

01:11:41.615 --> 01:11:44.446
get their Realization very well.

01:11:44.446 --> 01:11:46.716
May God bless you.

01:11:46.716 --> 01:11:55.574
Also if you want to come and meet Me you can
come on the stage, I would like to talk to

01:11:55.599 --> 01:11:56.599
you.

01:12:02.319 --> 01:12:03.319
So many!

01:12:03.344 --> 01:12:05.413
Now what do you want?

01:12:05.595 --> 01:12:09.645
The England, the whole England!

01:12:09.645 --> 01:12:15.416
Those who want to be should come, one by one,
please.
